\c 24
\p
\v 1 Zvino Bharamu wakati aona kuti zvakanaka pameso aJehovha kuropafadza Israeri, haana kuenda\add zve\add* sepane dzimwe nguva kusangana neun'anga\x + 23.3,15.\x*, asi wakataridza chiso chake kurenje.
\v 2 Zvino Bharamu wakasimudza meso ake ndokuona Israeri agere nemarudzi ake\x + 2.2-31.\x*; Mweya waMwari ndokuva pamusoro pake\x + Vato. 3.10; 1 Zvak. 19.20,23. 2 Makor. 15.1; 20.14.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino wakasimudza mufananidzo wake ndokuti: Chirevo chaBharamu mwanakomana waBheori\x + 2 Zvak. 23.1.\x*, nechirevo chemurume weziso rake rakasvinura.
\v 4 Chirevo chaiye anonzwa mashoko aMwari, anoona chiratidzo cheWemasimbaose, achiwa, uye akasvinudzwa meso ake\x + 1 Zvak. 19.24. Eze. 1.28; 3.23? Zvak. 1.10,17.\x*.
\v 5 Akanaka sei matende ako, haiwa Jakove, misha yako, haiwa Israeri!
\v 6 Semipata zvakaparadzirwa, semabindu kunhivi dzerwizi, semagavakava\x + Map. 1.3. Jer. 17.8.\x* Jehovha aakasima, semisidhari pedo nemvura\x + Map. 104.16.\x*.
\v 7 Mvura inoyerera inobva pazvirongo zvake, nembeu yake \add zvichava\add* pamvura zhinji\x + Jer. 51.13. Zvak. 17.1.\x*; namambo wake achakurira Agagi\x + 24.20. 1 Zvak. 15.8.\x*, neumambo hwake huchazvisimudzira\x + 2 Zvak. 5.12. 1 Makor. 14.2.\x*.
\v 8 Mwari akamubudisa kubva Egipita; ane simba serakaita renyati\x + 23.22.\x*; achadya vahedheni \add ivo\add* vavengi vake\x + 14.9; 23.24.\x*, uye achavhuna mapfupa avo\x + Eze. 23.34; Isa. 38.13. Jer. 50.17.\x*, neku\add va\add*bvoora nemiseve yake\x + 24.17. Map. 45.5. Jer. 50.9.\x*.
\v 9 Azvambarara, anorara pasi seshumba uye seshumbakadzi; ndiani achamumutsa\x + Gen. 49.9. Num. 23.24.\x*? Anokuropafadza ngaaropafadzwe, neanokutuka ngaatukwe\x + Gen. 12.3; 27.29.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zvino hasha dzaBharaki dzakapfutira Bharamu, iye ndokuzvirova maoko\x + Eze. 21.12. Job. 27.23. Marir. 2.15.\x*; Bharaki ndokuti kuna Bharamu: Ndakudanira kutuka vavengi vangu, asi tarira, waropafadza nekuropafadza\x + 23.11.\x* katatu aka.
\v 11 Naizvozvo ikozvino iwe tizira kunzvimbo yako; ndaiti ndichakukudza nekukudza; asi tarira, Jehovha wakudzivirira kurukudzo\x + 22.17,37.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino Bharamu wakati kuna Bharaki: Handina kutaurawo kunhume dzako dzawakatuma kwandiri here ndichiti:
\v 13 Kana Bharaki akandipa imba yake izere nesirivha negoridhe, handingagoni kudarika murairo waJehovha\x + 22.18.\x*, kuita zvakanaka kana zvakaipa nemoyo wangu; zvinotaura Jehovha ndizvo zvandichataura\x + 16.28.\x*?
\v 14 Zvino ikozvino tarira, ndinoenda kuvanhu vekwangu; uya ndigokuraira kuti vanhu ava vachaitei kuvanhu vekwenyu\x + Mik. 6.5\x* pamazuva ekupedzisira\x + Gen. 49.1. Dhan. 10.14.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Zvino wakasimudza mufananidzo wake ndokuti\x + 24.3,20,23; 21.27; 23.7.\x*: Chirevo chaBharamu mwanakomana waBheori\x + 24.3,4.\x*, nechirevo chemurume weziso rakasvinura.
\v 16 Chirevo chaiye anonzwa mashoko aMwari\x + 24.3,4.\x*, nekuziva zivo yeWekumusoro-soro, anoona chiratidzo cheWemasimbaose, achiwa, uye akasvinudzwa meso ake.
\v 17 Ndichamuona, asi kwete ikozvino\x + 23.9.\x*; ndichamutarisa, asi kwete pachiri pedo\x + 23.9.\x*; kuchabuda nyeredzi kubva\x + Job. 9.8. Mik. 1.3.\x* kuna Jakove\x + Mat. 2.2. Zvak. 22.16.\x*, netsvimbo yeushe ichasimuka kubva kuna Israeri\x + Gen. 49.10.\x*; ichabvovora miganhu yaMoabhu, nekuparadza vana vose vaSheti.
\v 18 Zvino Edhomu ichava nhaka \add yake\x + 2 Zvak. 8.14. Map. 60.8,9,12.\x*\add*, neSeiri ichava nhaka yevavengi vake\x + Gen. 32.3.\x*; asi Israeri achaita nesimba\x + Gen.15.19.\x*.
\v 19 Kuchabva kuna Jakove achatungamirira, uye achaparadza wakasara muguta.
\p
\v 20 Paakatarisa Amareki, wakasimudza mufananidzo wake ndokuti: Amareki ndewekutanga wevahedheni, asi kuguma kwake kuparara nekusingaperi.
\p
\v 21 Paakatarisa vaKeni, wakasimudza mufananidzo wake ndokuti: Hwakasimba ugaro hwako, dendere rako wakariisa paruware.
\v 22 Zvakadaro Kaini achaparadzwa, kusvika Ashuri akutapa.
\p
\v 23 Zvino wakasimudza mufananidzo wake ndokuti: Haiwa! Ndiani achararama kana Mwari achiita izvi?
\v 24 Zvino zvikepe \add zvichabva\add* kumahombekombe eKitimi\x + Dhan. 11.30. Gen. 10.4.\x*, zvigorwadza Ashuri, nekurwadza Ebheri\x + Gen. 10.21,25.\x*; naiyewo achaparadzwa nekusingaperi\x + 24.20.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Zvino Bharamu wakasimuka ndokuenda ndokudzokera kunzvimbo yake; naBharaki akaendawo nenzira yake\x + 31.8.\x*.
